extendedInfo.description: - requires Frozen Bubble 1.4Create, play and share your own levels-on-screen drawing-40 new levels you can play right away (menu->start frozen bubble)-download new level packs Frozen Bubble Level Editor will allow you to further extend joy of playing Frozen Bubble. Editor comes packed with 40 custom levels that you can play right away! By simple finger-drawing you can create your own levels. Get inspired by loading original levels, or make new ones from scratch. Created levels can be afterwards played in original Frozen Bubble. Editor and game cooperates together thanks to Pawel Aleksander Fedorynski, author of Android's port of Frozen Bubble. After you're done creating, upload your creations to server for other users. They can download and play your level packs. Let's see who is the most creative one ;)THIS IS LEVEL EDITOR NOT GAME ITSELF! PLS RUN TUTORIAL VIDEO BEFORE GIVING 1 STARPLEASE SEND ME AN EMAIL FROM APP IF YOU HAVE ANY PROBLEMS WITH IT. I CANNOT REPLY TO COMMENTS!
